{"tid":1191883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普指月球屬火星一部分被批欠常識","createTime":"2019-06-08T07:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T07:45:42.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"412d36d0a0e96180d0e1ebbc096a879eb78bcbce","tid":1191883,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:02:03.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國總統特朗普發帖文抨擊太空總署的登月計劃，其中一句聲稱月球是火星的一部分，被批評欠缺常識。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在社交網站發文，指美國五十年前已經成功登月，太空總署不應該再說要登月，而是應該專注於更大的事情，包括火星、國防和科學，提到火星時，他特別附加一句，指月球是火星的一部分。<br />\n<br />\n這番言論在網上引發熱議，不少網民都取笑特朗普無常識，連民主黨全國委員會亦發官方聲明回應，指月球並非火星的一部分。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普上月才表態支持美國重返月球，指他已經向太空總署額外增撥16億美元，推動再登月計劃，下一步就是火星。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=350933&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D350933%26refer%3D&d=Bm7f%2FS52JQW29R4IancW8%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=0a5393e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D350933%26refer%3D&h=5c2abecc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=350933&amp;refer=</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a3fb19413be5dbeab34488b485851e0d1f93cf","tid":1191883,"uid":20816,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:03:14.000Z","m